Class AdaptiveGrid<S extends Solution<?>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.uma.jmetal.util.AdaptiveGrid<S>

  • public class AdaptiveGrid<S extends Solution<?>>
extends Object

        public void updateGrid(S solution,
                       List<S> solutionSet)
